sequenceDiagram
    participant Analyst as Analyst
    participant MetricsSvc as Metrics Service
    participant AISystem as AI System
    participant AutonomyEval as Autonomy Evaluator
    participant PerfIndicators as AI Performance Indicators
    participant BusinessSys as Business Systems
    participant ImpactCalc as Business Impact Calculator
    participant DataWH as Data Warehouse
    participant Dashboard as Metrics Dashboard

    Analyst->>MetricsSvc: Request performance metrics beyond KPIs
    activate MetricsSvc

    MetricsSvc->>AISystem: Fetch AI operational logs
    activate AISystem
    AISystem-->>MetricsSvc: Logs, decisions, confidence scores
    deactivate AISystem

    MetricsSvc->>AutonomyEval: Compute autonomy-grade metrics
    activate AutonomyEval
    AutonomyEval-->>MetricsSvc: Autonomy level score
    deactivate AutonomyEval

    MetricsSvc->>PerfIndicators: Compute AI performance indicators
    activate PerfIndicators
    PerfIndicators-->>MetricsSvc: Accuracy, latency, drift, reliability
    deactivate PerfIndicators

    MetricsSvc->>BusinessSys: Fetch business outcome data
    activate BusinessSys
    BusinessSys-->>MetricsSvc: Revenue, cost, churn, satisfaction
    deactivate BusinessSys

    MetricsSvc->>ImpactCalc: Calculate business impact metrics
    activate ImpactCalc
    ImpactCalc-->>MetricsSvc: ROI, uplift, risk mitigation
    deactivate ImpactCalc

    MetricsSvc->>DataWH: Store aggregated metrics
    activate DataWH
    DataWH-->>MetricsSvc: Storage confirmation
    deactivate DataWH

    MetricsSvc-->>Dashboard: Publish metrics for visualization
    deactivate MetricsSvc

    Dashboard-->>Analyst: Display autonomy, AI performance, business impact